en_182060_0	Newly promoted four Majors General this morning (11) paid a joint courtesy call on the Commander of the Army, Lieutenant General Mahesh Senanayake at the Army Headquarters.
en_182060_1	Those new rankers, Major General Chandana Gunawardana, Commandant, Officer Career Development Centre - Buttala, Major General Wasantha Kumarapperuma, General Officer Commanding, 65 Division, Major General Jayantha Gunarathna, General Officer Commanding, 55 Division, Major General Deepthi Jayatilake, General officer Commanding, 12 Division received warm greetings and best wishes of the Army Commander before interactive discussions set in.
en_182060_2	Before they ended the courtesy meeting, they added memories by sitting with the Commander for a group photo.
